{# LLM extracts structured order data from conversation. Output: items (name, quantity, modifiers), customerName, customerPhone, fulfillmentType, scheduledTime, specialInstructions, missingFields. #}
{% set menu = GetCustomerAttribute(field="project_attributes_menu_items") %}
{{system}}
Extract order details from the conversation. The restaurant menu is:
<Menu>
{{menu}}
</Menu>

<Conversation>
{{memory}}
</Conversation>

<LatestAgentResponse>
{{agentAnswer}}
</LatestAgentResponse>

Output ONLY valid JSON with this exact structure (no markdown, no extra text):
{"items": [{"name": "item name", "quantity": 1, "price": 0, "modifiers": []}], "customerName": "", "customerPhone": "", "fulfillmentType": "pickup or delivery", "scheduledTime": "ISO datetime or empty", "specialInstructions": "", "missingFields": []}

Rules:
- items: array of {name, quantity, price (from menu if available else 0), modifiers (array of strings)}
- customerName, customerPhone: from conversation; empty string if not mentioned
- fulfillmentType: "pickup" or "delivery"
- scheduledTime: when they want the order, or empty
- specialInstructions: any special requests
- missingFields: list of field names still needed (e.g. ["customerPhone"] if phone not given)
{{end}}
{{assistant}}
{% set result = Gen(temperature=0.1, maxTokens=2000, topP=0, skipFilter=True) %}
{{end}}
{{ Return(val=result) }}
